ComicInfo.Title: Miss Brutality / Case Closed / Warehouse Find / Nerves of Steel
ComicInfo.Summary:
Featuring four short stories! Juri faces off against the deadly doll Decapre! Ibuki battles the mysterious Q! Sakura and Dan get down to some serious training, and Chun-li tangles with the Mad Gear Gang! It's a truly legendary gathering of rare tales in Street Fighter's first Annual 1-shot!
Story TitlesMiss BrutalityCase ClosedWarehouse FindNerves of Steel*List of covers and their creators:* Cover | Name | Creator(s) | Sidebar Location | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- A | Cover A | Rob Porter | 1 | B | Cover B | Rob Porter | 2 | C | 1:10 Retailer Incentive Homage Cover C | Hans Steinbach | 3 | Notes:
The four stories in this annual were originally published as bonus stories in four collection: Street Fighter Legends: Sakura, Street Fighter Legends: Chun-Li, Street Fighter Legends: Ibuki and Street Fighter IV so the events that happen in these stories tales place before the Street Fighter Unlimited series.The 1:10 Retailer Inceentive Homage cover C is a homage to the cover of Giant-Size X-Men #1.
